    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is being offered as a practical budget option for the right buyer. It starts, runs, and presents a good opportunity for someone seeking basic transportation, a project car, or a low-cost extra vehicle. Priced with its overall condition in mind and represented honestly, this is a chance to secure dependable value without a big upfront investment.",
