    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but if you\u2019re after cheap, simple transport or a solid project to tinker with, this one has real potential. Great option for someone handy or anyone wanting an affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune. Priced to sell and open to sensible interest.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and a chassis that still feels composed on the road. Shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but it starts, moves, and stops well, making it an ideal commuter, backup car, or weekend project. Cabin is usable, major mechanical bits feel serviceable, and it has the kind of honest, straightforward character that\u2019s getting harder to find. Great value for someone who wants affordable transportation with real potential.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
