      "description": "Cheap ride. Runs and gets you there. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Turn heads and spark ideas with a car that wears its story proudly. This is the kind of ride for someone who sees potential everywhere\u2014a dependable project, a practical around-town companion, or a budget-friendly set of wheels with real personality. It has a lived-in charm and an honest presence that makes every drive feel a little more interesting. If you want something affordable, distinctive, and ready for its next chapter, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers straightforward value for anyone seeking dependable basic transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age, but it remains an affordable way to get into a vehicle without stretching your budget. A practical choice for a commuter, first-time buyer, or handy owner looking for a smart buy.",
