    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a great little project to tinker with. It has the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect, and it\u2019s being priced accordingly. If you want something approachable, practical, and easy on the wallet, this could be a really smart buy.",
      "price": 6900.0,
